{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/Check_Clean_Resized.gif?t=1736929098\" /><strong>Check&amp;Clean is a tactical First Person Shooter blending music, speedrun elements and intense action. It immerses you in a rhythmic universe, alternating analysis sequences and gunfights. The innovative music coordination allows players to synchronize explosive moments with beats.\u00a0</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will have multiple tools to escape your robbery nightmare: <strong>Weapons, C4, cameras, ammunition boxes and mines</strong>. Take care of analyzing different rooms before entering in. Informations are crucial in our game. You will not survive if you enter a room without analyzing environment first. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u00ab Every night, I have the same nightmare. I\u2019m pulling a heist. Stuck in a room, there is only one exit : a locked door. It can be a hotel, an office, a basement, or a laboratory. But everytime, it begins the same way\u2026 I choose a weapon. \u00bb</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MUSIC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The innovative music coordination allows players to synchronize explosive moments with beats.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/MusicLoop.gif?t=1736929098\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WEAPONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are several weapons you can unlock by completing levels. Each weapon can be customized and adapted to your style with unlockable In-Game attachments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/Customization.gif?t=1736929098\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CAMERAS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In each level, there are 5 cameras giving you perspective to 5 different rooms. Cameras allow you to anticipate enemies position, ammo boxes position, and mines position. <strong>CHECK !</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/Cameras_Resized.gif?t=1736929098\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">C4</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use C4 to destroy doors and clean areas. Pay attention to know all the details hidden behind the door before destroying it. <strong>CLEAN !</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/ExplodeDoor.gif?t=1736929098\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">AMMUNITION BOX</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different ammunition boxes are concealed in the rooms. You won\u2019t survive without finding them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/AmmoBox_Resized.gif?t=1736929098\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MINES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Several mines are hidden in the rooms. Be extremely vigilant, and use them to your advantage. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/Mines.gif?t=1736929098\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">RANDOMIZATION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check&amp;Clean also claims to be a memory game. There are several randomization systems to force the player to analyze their environment and optimize the replayability experience. Randomization affects enemy positions, ammunition boxes position, and mines position. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368840/extras/Randomization.gif?t=1736929098\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2368840?t=1736929098","backgrou